WEBVTT

00:00:00.722 --> 00:00:04.212
We need to build
a weather service for water.

00:00:04.236 --> 00:00:07.610
Yet, until we collectively
demand accountability,

00:00:07.634 --> 00:00:10.470
the incentives to fund it will not exist.

00:00:11.805 --> 00:00:16.744
The first time I spoke at a conference
was here at TED, eight years ago.

00:00:16.768 --> 00:00:19.056
Fresh out of grad school,
little did I know

00:00:19.080 --> 00:00:20.934
that in those few minutes onstage,

00:00:20.958 --> 00:00:23.492
I was framing the questions
I was going to be asked

00:00:23.516 --> 00:00:24.791
for the next decade.

00:00:25.599 --> 00:00:28.111
And, like too many 20-somethings,

00:00:28.135 --> 00:00:30.611
I expected to solve
the world's problems --